<P>> ...because I've been having much fun on Rallos Zek. In UO the pk

<BR>&gt; situation along with the bugs and exploits got way outta hand.
<BR>&gt; But so far, the PvP server seems to have curtailed the abuse for
<BR>&gt; the most part and really made it quite playable. I for one,
<BR>&gt; would not want to play on a server that doesnt offer the
<BR>&gt; adrenalin rush of PvP combat.
<P>&gt; You just cant beat the feeling of being out in the wilderness
<BR>&gt; and coming across someone that, a few weeks earlier, killed you
<BR>&gt; while you were being swarmed by monsters...or blindsided you
<BR>&gt; with his entire gang while you were alone or vastly outnumbered.
<BR>&gt; Revenge can be so sweet.
<P>You are SOOO right :) Well written!
<P>-Gray
